    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://newyork.craigslist.org/que/lab/6042141841.html"></div>
        </div>
Hello potential applicants,<br>
<br>
We (John and Ashley) are seeking a Personal Assistant that would be able to assist us with the following items:<br>
<br>
<br>
General Housekeeping<br>
<br>
Washing Dishes<br>
General Cleaning<br>
Vacuuming<br>
Dusting<br>
Closet/Drawer Organization<br>
Ironing<br>
Trash collection<br>
<br>
<br>
Cooking<br>
<br>
Cooking/storing lunch and dinner for the week<br>
Planning dietary needs<br>
<br>
<br>
Package Pickup/Delivery<br>
<br>
Ordering/Organizing Groceries<br>
Folding/Organizing laundry<br>
Sending/Organizing Snail mail<br>
<br>
<br>
Odd Jobs<br>
<br>
Company Research<br>
Product Research<br>
Posting to Job boards<br>
Responding to Job ads<br>
Travel planning<br>
Bill Pay<br>
Other intermediary 1-off tasks<br>
<br>
We have a schedule set up that will generally ask for ~10 hours of work per week. Please give us your availability so we can plan accordingly.<br>
<br>
<br>
Our assistant needs to be a true go-getter. Trustworthiness, Adaptability and Organization skills are paramount in this position. <br>
<br>
We need an assistant that is tech-savvy. On occasion, you may be asked to conduct research on a certain company or product and we need you to be able to prepare reports that follow set guidelines. You will also be asked to serve as a personal recruiter posting resumes to job boards and applying to positions as our representative. In this endeavor, attention to detail and literacy are key. Your application to this post will serve as evidence of your ability to represent yourself and others well. Give it your best. Also, please include the word "Thorough" at the top of your response email so we know that you actually read our full requirements before applying. <br>
<br>
Experience cooking large amounts of food is necessary. We need someone who can preemptively cook 10 lunches and 10 dinners for the week ahead. (1 lunch meal and 1 dinner meal per person for each weekday.) We will take care of weekends ourselves. Please give us an estimate on how many hours it will take you to prepare said amount of food and what types of food you have experience cooking. <br>
<br>
Please note we will be conducting background checks on our applicants and will require that you have experience with independent contractor or personal employee tax requirements. Frankly, we are inexperienced with the legal procedure on paying a personal employee or independent contractor. If you could walk us through the process we will be eager to follow along and pay you for your time spent researching once you have secured the position.<br>
<br>
Lastly, we need to be able to get along with our assistant. Give us a background of what you like in an employer, and what drives you crazy. (Feel free to share positive or negative anecdotes) Let us know what you like to do in your free time as well as an insight into your aspirations and goals for the future. <br>
<br>
<br>
In short, send us:<br>
<br>
-Your resume<br>
-Your availability<br>
-Predicted hours to cook weekly meals<br>
-Previous types of dishes served<br>
-Personal Insight <br>
-Any other information you think would help us make our decision<br>
<br>
<br>
Thank you for your interest and good luck.<br>
<br>
Wishing you a successful rest of the day,<br>
<br>
John + Ashley    </section>

